  "faqQ1": "How do I set appointment reminders?",
  "faqA1": "You can set appointment reminders by navigating to the \"Appointments\" section, selecting your scheduled visit, and tapping the \"Set Reminder\" option. You will be able to choose a time interval (e.g., 1 day or 1 hour before).",
  "faqQ2": "Is my health data secure?",
  "faqA2": "Yes. We use industry-leading encryption and follow HIPAA/GDPR compliance guidelines to ensure your personal health information remains private and secure. Data is stored anonymously on secure servers.",
  "faqQ3": "How do I change my due date?",
  "faqA3": "If you are tracking a pregnancy, you can change your estimated due date (EDD) in the \"Profile\" or \"Tracking\" settings. Tap on the current due date field to manually enter a new date based on your latest ultrasound or doctor's recommendation.",
  "faqQ4": "Can I export my health records?",
  "faqA4": "Yes! Go to Settings > Data & Privacy > Download My Data to export all your information in a readable format.",
  "faqQ5": "How do I contact support?",
  "faqA5": "You can contact support via the \"Contact Support\" button at the bottom of this screen, or you can email us directly at support@appname.com. We typically respond within 24 hours.",
  "faqQ6": "What languages are supported?",
  "faqA6": "Currently, the app supports English, French, and Arabic. You can change your preferred language in the \"App Settings\" menu.",
